  "title": "6723 - English Language Tutor (Early Childhood / Preschool)",
  "description": "<p><strong>English Language Tutor (Early Childhood / Preschool)</strong></p><ul><li><p>Working Days: 6 working days (include Saturday & Sunday)</p></li><li><p>Working Timing: 9am to 8pm (Weekday), 9am to 6pm (weekend)</p></li><li><p>Basic Salary: $4000 Monthly</p></li><li><p>Address: Tanjong Pagar</p></li><li><p><strong>Bachelor’s degree</strong> and <strong>at least 3 years</strong> of teaching experience.</p></li><li><p>Willingness to work during evenings, weekends, public holidays and peak periods</p></li></ul><p></p><p><u><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></u></p><ul><li><p>Preparing English language lessons plans, and tailor the lessons to students’ needs</p></li><li><p>Providing (written) feedback on student progress</p></li><li><p>Developing curriculum materials</p></li><li><p>Identifying learning obstacles</p></li><li><p>Supervising students during peak hours</p></li><li><p>Other ad hoc tasks</p></li></ul><p></p><p><br /><strong>📲 Interested candidates, please WhatsApp your resume to: +65 9642 0989 (Han)</strong><br /><strong>📧 Or email your resume to: </strong><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/6723-sales-support-customer-care-executive-sgd-2600%E2%80%934000-industrial-services-north-area-post-sales-support-supreme-hr-advisory-a212f1138e3ddd0ad8ec472e0fc6a5d6/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</a><strong></strong></p><p><strong>👤 Chaw Chiaw Han | R22106723 🏢 The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</strong></p>",
